out overcoming the lack of memory bandwidth implied in using H800s instead =
of H100s. Moreover, if you actually did the math on the previous question, =
you would realize that DeepSeek actually had an excess of computing; that's=
 because DeepSeek actually programmed 20 of the 132 processing units on eac=
